headline: Chewy (CHWY) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Chewy (CHWY) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 14.46% and 1.29%, respectively, for the quarter ended April 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
